tioned [here](https://github.com/nikitabobko/AeroSpace/issues/556#issuecomment-2392419701) fixes the `PATH` on the Intel Mac, but setting it removes the `/opt/homebrew` paths, which unfortunately then breaks the `PATH` on Apple Silicon Macs:\n```\nPATH=/usr/local/bin/:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin\n```","files":null}]}